    <item>
      <title>Vulcanus —The Volcanic Planet Foundry Guide</title>
      <link>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/vulcanus-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 16:52:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://factorioguides.com/space-age/vulcanus-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Vulcanus is a volcanic wasteland where normal smelting doesn&#39;t work. &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/steel_furnace.png&#34; alt=&#34;steel_furnace&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Steel&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; Stone furnaces and &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/icon/steel_furnace.png&#34; alt=&#34;steel_furnace&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Steel&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; steel furnaces are useless here. The foundry is your only path to metal.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR:&lt;/strong&gt; Foundries smelt ore using calcite (from volcanic ash recycling). Vulcanus yields tungsten carbide, the key to Productivity Module 4. Import everything else —Vulcanus is a specialized mining world.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://factorioguides.com/images/diagrams/foundry-cycle.svg&#34; alt=&#34;Vulcanus foundry system —ore processing, ash recycling loop, and tungsten carbide production&#34; class=&#34;schema-diagram&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-foundry-system&#34;&gt;The Foundry System&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Foundries replace furnaces on Vulcanus. They require three inputs: ore, calcite, and fuel.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
